window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>\"I'm not in the rescue business,\" states Jonathon Hunter, to the amusement of his crew.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>But rescues are the least of his concerns.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>Darkness is coming, and there are still people out there who don't like him.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>The Sirius system has always fascinated Jon, and he is drawn to solve its mysteries.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>But what is the price of being curious? Can one simple step cause what you dread the most? Is it possible to do one too many rescues? To take one step too far into the unknown?&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>For those who take that one step too many; be they foolhardy, curious, or simply unlucky; hope takes the shape of the Hero to the Rescue.</p>"; 
